      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in Carbon Black over Cinnamon leather. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and a precision Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanically flawless, the double-VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rear subframe has been reinforced\u2014addressing the chassis's primary vulnerabilities. The limited-slip differential remains tight, and the suspension retains its factory-spec damping and rebound characteristics. Every bushing is pliable, and the undercarriage is free of oxidation. This is a turn-key collector piece for the discerning driver who values high-revving atmospheric induction and telepathic steering feedback.",
